%description
The libfm package contains a library used to develop file managers providing some file management utilities.
%package 	devel
Group:          Development/Libraries
Summary:        Headers and static lib for application development
Requires:	%{name} = %{version}
Requires:	gtk2-devel menu-cache-devel
%description 	devel
Install this package if you want do compile applications using the pcre
library.
%prep
%setup -q
%patch0 -p1
%build
./configure --prefix=%{_prefix} --sysconfdir=%{_sysconfdir} \
	    --disable-static
make %{?_smp_mflags}
%install
make DESTDIR=%{buildroot} install
%files
%defattr(-,root,root)
%{_sysconfdir}/*
%{_bindir}/*
%{_libdir}/*
%exclude %{_libdir}/*.la
%exclude %{_libdir}/debug
%{_datadir}/*
%files devel
%defattr(-,root,root)
%{_includedir}/*
%{_libdir}/*.la
